name: Red Flame (part 1)
description:
I have always been more on the masculine side. Tom boy till I die. This is the first part of the collection. 

I have recently discovered that I jive more with being bisexual than straight. Personally the way my brain has picked up things since I was a kid I would've thought I realized this sooner. 

The colors in this collection reflect anger, passion, sex, and desire for the beautiful women.
